dc_title_s: City of Camden, NJ river front map, 1865.
dc_description_s: Map of Camden city water front from Coopers Point to Kaighns Point, along with the water front of Philadelphia PA. Map includes water depths in feet based on soundings taken in the Delaware River. Other information on map includes some company names of buildings and demarcations of 1832 low water line and original high water line. Map was part of a Report of the Commissioners to the Legislature of the State of New Jersey.
